article_text: The Covered California bus stopped Wednesday at Modesto’s McHenry Village on the 10th day of a scheduled nine-day tour of the state. The health benefits exchange extended the tour for an extra day to deliver the feel-good message that affordable health insurance is available for all.

article_summary:
The Covered California bus stopped Wednesday at Modesto’s McHenry Village on the 10th day of a scheduled nine-day tour of the state.
The health benefits exchange extended the tour for an extra day to deliver the feel-good message that affordable health insurance is available for all.
